comments:
Created 1.4.1990 out of the parishes of Great Amwell, Little 
    Amwell, Stanstead St Margarets and Ware. See also Table 2, note (c).

Abolished 1.4.1990 and added to the parish of Hertford 
    Heath, See also Table 2, note (a).

Created 1.4.1974 by renaming the parish of Ware Urban. See also 
    Table 2, notes (b) and (c).
Renamed 2.5.1991 to become the parish of Wareside. See also Table 2, note (b).
Created 2.5.1991 by renaming the parish of Ware Rural. See also Table 2, note (c).
